        <mxCell id="40" value="CHECK logic:&#xa;- SCAN/SRST + last line + last OE + last ch -&gt; FWAIT&#xa;- SCAN/SRST + last line + last OE + more ch -&gt; LWAIT (tail dummy)&#xa;- last OE in group -&gt; LWAIT, line_cnt += DUAL_BY_MODEL&#xa;- more OE in group -&gt; OE_READY, oe_cnt++&#xa;- TRST -&gt; FWAIT&#xa;&#xa;ch advance: if num &lt; GATE_NUM/DUAL-1 and&#xa;ch_cnt &gt;= GATE_CH-dummy_add-1: num++, ch=0&#xa;else: ch_cnt += dummy_add+1" style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=8;align=left;spacingLeft=5;verticalAlign=top;spacingTop=3;" vertex="1" parent="1">
